title: /R E P E A T -- Media Advisory: Federal Election news on newswire.ca/
text:
CNW Group Ltd.
MONTREAL , Oct. 19, 2015 /CNW Telbec/ - CNW has grouped all news releases related to the Federal Election . For the convenience of researchers and news media covering this topic, Federal Budget is a Hot Topic on newswire.ca.
Several organizations issue news releases prior to and following the elections.
For news releases and multimedia assets related to the Federal Election 2015, visit:
http://www.newswire.ca/news-releases/federal-election-2015-320423512.html
